query:
SELECT se.subjectId, se.professorId, 
       (SELECT id FROM subjects WHERE id = se.subjectId LIMIT 1) as subject_exists,
       (SELECT userId FROM subjects WHERE id = se.subjectId LIMIT 1) as subject_owner
FROM student_enrollments se 
WHERE se.studentId = 1
LIMIT 5;
